Although Ticket Xpress was primarily created as a service to NYU School of Medicine students, Ticket Xpress is also open to all graduate students, Medical Center & Bellevue employees and volunteers, alumni and NYU Washington Square students and staff. Tickets are available for many Broadway plays, operas, ballets, sporting events, movies and much more. Ticket Xpress also has shirts, mugs, coupon books and a variety of periodicals with information about events around the City.   NYU School of Medicine student IDs are required for the student discount. Tickets are sold on a first-come, first-serve basis. The ticket office accepts cash or checks with two forms of ID, and credit cards which have a processesing fee for each item that you purchase.   Location  The Ticket Xpress Office is currently located at 545 First Ave., Greenberg Hall, Suite 6E  Tuesday-Thursday, 3:30pm-5:00pm  Friday - 11:00am-12:30pm   Click here to see our current offerings!   For the current ticket listing sales recording, call (212) 263-2899.   To speak with someone in the Ticket Xpress Box Office, call (212) 263-3028.
